ocedures and forms. (a) *␣*␣* The Director may, for good cause and to the extent permitted by statute, waive the applicability of any provision of this chapter. * * * * * PART 506_INFORMATION COLLECTION REQUIREMENTS UNDER THE PAPERWORK REDUCTION ACT 3. The authority citation for part 506 continues to read as follows: Authority: 44 U.S.C. 3501 et seq . 4. Section 506.1 is amended by adding in numerical order one new entry to the table in paragraph (b) to read as follows: §506.1 OMB control numbers assigned pursuant to the Paperwork Reduction Act. * * * * *
